@calkinsclan666

You don't need the "Auto Reset".
All you need to do now is to remove Norton using Norton Removal Tool.
Then install back the Norton 2010.
Disable Norton Tamper Protection thing, run the crack as Administrator (I believe u already know this).
Install the 366 days. Don't click yes on the auto-trial reset.
Then after it's done and you can see that you have 366 days of subscription, UNINSTALL the Trial Reset.
Then u're done.
